Choose maximum installation of the game if you intend to apply mods

Apply official 1.02 Patch (most mods and extras are designed for this version)

Uninstall Codecs (VERY IMPORTANT)

Try not to die (moderately important)

Apply XP patch if uninstalling codecs does not help

Apply chocobo patch (will save problems later on)

Possibly find a multipatcher (on the site i mentioned earlier) to save you hassle

Do not buy a sword and swing it around like cloud, you will die, it will then not matter if the game works or not.

